Titolo: Haunting (video game)

Anno: 1993

Descrizione: Haunting Starring Polterguy is a 1993 comedy-horror video game released for the Sega Mega Drive/Genesis by Electronic Arts.  Taking control of a ghost named 'Polterguy', the player must bring various household items to life in order to frighten a family away from their home.
The game is notable for an extensive array of short animation sequences.  A port for the PlayStation Portable was released in 2006 on EA Replay.